# Agentic Program with LangChain

## Overview

This project implements an intelligent agent that can analyze user messages, determine whether they are questions or requests to generate/edit content, and respond accordingly. The agent can:

1. Answer questions directly in the terminal
2. Generate code in various programming languages
3. Edit existing code files
4. Generate text content
5. Edit existing text content

## Project Structure

```
agentic-program/
├── main.py                 # Entry point for the application
├── config.py               # Configuration settings
├── requirements.txt        # Python dependencies
├── README.md               # Project documentation
├── src/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── input_handler.py    # Handles user input
│   ├── intent_analyzer.py  # Analyzes user intent
│   ├── task_router.py      # Routes tasks to appropriate handlers
│   ├── handlers/
│   │   ├── __init__.py
│   │   ├── question_handler.py  # Handles direct questions
│   │   ├── code_handler.py      # Handles code generation/editing
│   │   └── text_handler.py      # Handles text generation/editing
│   └── response_generator.py    # Generates response summaries
└── output/                 # Directory for generated files
    ├── code/               # Generated code files
    └── text/               # Generated text files
```